      <title>意大利电信盈利因企业服务和巴西业务增长而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/telecom-italia-earnings-rise-on-enterprise-services-brazil-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利电信 (Telecom Italia SpA) 是第一家出售其固定电话网络的欧洲电话运营商，该公司公布初步盈利增长，这得益于企业服务需求的不断增长以及其巴西子公司的强劲表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/telecom-italia-earnings-rise-on-enterprise-services-brazil-unit</guid>
